///
/// Main - introduction
@NODE INTRODUCTION "Introduction"

@{fg highlight}@{B}@{U}Introduction@{fg text}@{UB}@{UU}

 XBase is very flexible database with very easy fields and layout
 editor (you can delete, add or move field at any moment). This program
 uses dynamic memory management, which means that number of records and
 fields depends on amount of free memory.

FEATURES:

 - easy to use GUI (font sensitivity, shortcuts, tooltypes, appwindow,
   appicon, iconification, full localization, popup menus)
 - six kinds of fields
 - handle URL addresses using openurl.library
 - use system clipboard
 - full configurable fields
 - drag&drop layout editor
 - view and definition of fields can be modify at any moment
 - many kinds of fields for every project
 - localized sorting of records
 - flexible sort and search option
 - pattern or another operator can be used for searching record
 - configurable printing option
 - Save/load files in ASCII format (CSV and TSV)
 - ARexx port (over 90 commands)
 - ability to protect project at two levels
 - statistics option
 - on-line help
   ...

@ENDNODE
///
/// Main - installation
@NODE INSTALLATION "Installation on hard disk"

@{fg highlight}@{B}@{U}Installation on hard disk@{fg text}@{UB}@{UU}

To install the program on your harddisk, please copy program drawer to the
destination directory and install the icons (Add-ons/Icons/Install).

If you want to use the popupmenu, you must install popupmenu.library
(@{" Add-ons/PopupMenuUser/Install " SYSTEM "INSTALLER //Add-ons/PopupMenuUser/Install"}).

If you want to be able to call your web browser from program level,
you must install openurl.library (@{" Add-ons/OpenURL/Install" SYSTEM "INSTALLER //Add-ons/OpenURL/Install"}).


@ENDNODE
///
/// Main - requirements
@NODE REQUIREMENTS "Requirements"

@{fg highlight}@{B}@{U}Requirements@{fg text}@{UB}@{UU}

Program requirements:
  - Kickstart 3.0
  - 1 MB RAM

Program uses the following libraries:
  necessary:
    - asl.library         (system library)
    - control.gadget      (in archive)
    - textfield.gadget    (in archive)

  recommended:
    - openurl.gadget      (in archive)
    - popupmenu.gadget    (in archive)
    - titlebar.image      (in archive)
    - locale.library      (system library)
    - icon.library        (system library)
    - diskfont.library    (system library)
    - iffparse.library    (system library)
    - rexxsyslib.library  (system library)

@ENDNODE
